FT  25 APR 92 / Finance and the Family: Correction
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
LAST week's piece 'The O'Higgins road to riches' incorrectly said that Asda
had passed its final dividend. In fact it maintained its final payout and
cut its interim dividend.
