FT  24 APR 92 / Observer: Milking time
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Fancy being a gentleman, or gentlewoman farmer? All you need to go with your
green wellies is a bigger than average garden and Pounds 27.50, and the
National Farmers Union will welcome you to its flock with open arms.
