FT  24 APR 92 / UK Company News: Wyevale buying Lewes operation
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Wyevale Garden Centres is increasing the number of centres under operation
to 41 with the acquisition of Swanborough Garden Centre of Newhaven Road,
Lewes, Sussex, for about Pounds 1.78m.
Consideration will be satisfied from the proceeds of a placing of 946,872
shares at 171p each to raise Pounds 1.62m. The shares will not rank for the
final dividend.
